{"tid":796761,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"凍齡美女！阿仔快高長大 李嘉欣Keep住靚","createTime":"2018-08-28T03:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T08:26:49.000Z","uid":48905,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"228450f11d8cd069ab814ed1030797fbf31df07f","tid":796761,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:58:30.000Z","msg":"養尊處優嘅大美人李嘉欣現時主力照顧Jayden，呢日趁住假期，嘉欣就帶咗Jayden去藝術館參觀，仲影低唔少靚相做留念，嘉欣上載照片，留言話：「#weekend #familytime #大館#summer2018 #」相中所見，嘉欣雖然一身便服上陣，但仍然掩蓋唔到佢嘅高貴氣息！睇相仲一啲歲月痕迹都睇唔到，Keep得勁好！而Jayden雖然得個後尾枕出鏡，但都睇得出佢大個仔咗、高咗好多，不過見到佢側面有眼鏡框，睇嚟佢開始近視喇！ <br />\n<br />\n嘉欣除咗帶個仔去藝術館見識又同佢喺屋企整嘢食，可以話係用盡個假期，亦感受到兩母子關係非常密切！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/115743_d14084d8b457b9bd5a70d0aa0e5fa09a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F115743_d14084d8b457b9bd5a70d0aa0e5fa09a.png&h=ad573795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> 十年如一日！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/115744_64193b0cea17e880f0fd39cc984aee0c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F115744_64193b0cea17e880f0fd39cc984aee0c.png&h=91679971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> 一啲歲月痕迹都冇，仲愈來愈靚！</span>"},{"pid":"ac26e7cade24284ab3265d867f3670531e6abf6f","tid":796761,"uid":36296,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:00:41.000Z","msg":"依家快高長大唔好咩？"},{"pid":"6a12de5296b5aa3b6ff4c22a883977b62d620629","tid":796761,"uid":146604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b316988401e6769496c1f95cebb52484490aaf","tid":796761,"uid":48905,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家快高長大唔好咩？</blockquote><br />\n無諗住快高長大佢生來把撚呀？"